    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 33.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第33课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Out of the Darkness.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "冲出黑暗。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why was the girl in hospital?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "那个女孩为什么住院？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Nearly a week passed before the girl was able to explain what had happened to her.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "差不多过了一个星期，那个女孩才说清楚自己遭遇了什么。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "One afternoon, she set out from the coast in a small boat and was caught in a storm.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一天下午，她乘一条小船从海岸出发，途中遇上了暴风雨。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "Towards evening, the boat struck a rock and the girl jumped into the sea.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "傍晚时分，小船撞上礁石，女孩跳进了海里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Then she swam to the shore after spending the whole night in the water.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她在水里度过整整一夜后，游到了岸边。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "During that time, she covered a distance of eight miles.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在此期间，她游了八英里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Early next morning, she saw a light ahead.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第二天清晨，她看到前方有一盏灯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "She knew she was near the shore because the light was high up on the cliffs.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她知道自己已接近海岸，因为那盏灯高高地位于峭壁上。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "On arriving at the shore, the girl struggled up the cliff towards the light she had seen.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "到达岸边后，女孩挣扎着爬上峭壁，朝她看到的灯光走去。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "That was all she remembered.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她只记得这些。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "When she woke up a day later, she found herself in hospital.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "一天后醒来时，她发现自己躺在医院里。"
      }
    }
  ],
